PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions about PaperCup Trading
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: PaperCup Trading is an online marketplace where people can buy, sell and trade used paper cups. Whether you have a collection you want to sell or are looking for rare or unique cups, our platform connects buyers and sellers.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How does the trading process work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Sellers can list their paper cups for sale by providing detailed descriptions and photos. Buyers can browse listings, make offers, and complete purchases securely. Once a sale is made, the seller ships the cup to the buyer.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: We accept all major credit cards, PayPal, and cryptocurrency payments for maximum convenience and security for buyers and sellers.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Are there any fees for using PaperCup Trading?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We charge a small commission fee on completed sales to cover our operating costs. The fee rate is clearly displayed during the listing and checkout process.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Got questions about buying or selling paper cups? We've got answers!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What kinds of paper cups can I trade?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our marketplace supports trading of all types of paper cups - hot cups, cold cups, branded cups, plain cups. As long as it's made of paper and cup-shaped, you can buy or sell it here.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How do I list a paper cup for sale?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Just create an account, snap some photos of your cup, describe its condition and any unique features, set your price, and hit list! We'll take care of promoting your listing.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: What payment methods do you accept?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: We currently accept all major credit cards, PayPal, and cryptocurrency payments in Bitcoin and Ethereum for maximum buyer/seller convenience.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! Our team of paper cup experts carefully examines every listing before approving it on the marketplace to ensure you only get the real deal.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We offer a 30-day return window with free return shipping. Just let us know if your cup arrives damaged or not as described and we'll make it right.
